						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up by the road-side.</p>						

						<p>1117 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This record, engraved below No. 71/41-42 to the right, mentions <hi rend="italic">mūlasthāna.</hi> The extant portion of the record refers to the date, viz., <hi rend="bold">Chāḷukya-Vikrama year 42, Hēmaḷaṁbi, Bhādrapada-ba• • •</hi> These details are incomplete for verification. The date falls on some day in the month of <hi rend="bold">August of 1117 A.D.</hi></p>						

